title: Luo Hengyu
text: Luo Hengyu (born 22 December 1972) is a Chinese <a href="archery">archer</a>. He competed in the men's <a href="Archery%20at%20the%201996%20Summer%20Olympics%20%E2%80%93%20Men%27s%20individual">individual</a> and <a href="Archery%20at%20the%201996%20Summer%20Olympics%20%E2%80%93%20Men%27s%20team">team</a> events at the <a href="1996%20Summer%20Olympics">1996 Summer Olympics</a>.
